<span id="Description"></span>
==Popis==

Nástroj [[File:Spreadsheet_CreateSheet.svg|24px]] '''Vytvořit list''' přidá do aktuálního dokumentu nový list.

==Usage==

# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_CreateSheet.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_CreateSheet|New Spreadsheet]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Spreadsheet → [[File:Spreadsheet_CreateSheet.svg|16px]] New Spreadsheet}} option from the menu.
# Double-click the spreadsheet in the [[Tree_View|Tree View]] to open it on a new tab in the [[Main_View_Area|Main View Area]].
# Edit the contents of the cells.
# Close the spreadsheet tab when you are finished, the values are saved automatically as you type them.


